fields.title: Thor: Love and Thunder
fields.review: Watch along in cinema with my sister. I feel like it's a little bit messy in the plot, but still very funny and exciting to watch.

fields.title: Avengers Infinity War
fields.review: I think this film is one of the best films ever made by Marvel Studios. The highlight that I got after watching this film was the fun and cool CGI.

fields.title: Dilan 1990
fields.review: One of the good Indonesian films with the theme of teenage romance growing up. Maybe a little cringe because of the pick-up lines but still interesting to watch.

fields.title: Joker
fields.review: A film that is quite different because of a different point of view as well, which is to tell how a villain is born. Recommended.
